It turns out under those circumstances, the
difference between

95
00:06:33,349 --> 00:06:37,430
the check and the credit card was really low,
and, in fact, it was

96
00:06:37,430 --> 00:06:40,559
statistically not significant.

97
00:06:40,559 --> 00:06:43,559
But let's compare that with the green line
